         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <ab>Sacred to the Shades of the Dead. Greetings to you, traveler! If you wish to identify my inscription, I was Nigrio Aequidicus. I was healthy while I was alive, and I fared well. I devoted happy years to wine and to slumber. Ah, a wretch! A brief hour carried off so many things. Goodbye!</ab>
